 <div class="row">
    <div class="column left" style="background-color:rgba(147, 174, 144, 0.5); border:4px double #B4A9DA;">
      </br>
      <details>
        <summary> Where can I ride my scooter?</summary>
          <p> You can ride your scooter anywhere across the Nipmuc Notch area! Just be sure to return it to one of our 14 stations!</p>
      </details>
      </br>
      <details>
          <summary> I am visiting for a couple days. How do I use ValleyScoot?</summary>
          <div> You can sign up for an account on our website and then view our stations map to familiarize yourself with the area!</div>
      </details>
      </br>
      <details>
          <summary> Do I have to sign up to use a scooter? </summary>
          <div> Currently yes, as our system is interconnected through our website. Our team is actively working on implementing a card or cash system for stations with in-person rental kiosks as well!</div>
      </details>
      </br>
      <details>
      <summary> How long can I rent a scooter? </summary>
        <p> You can rent a scooter for as long as you want, but be aware that while in use it accumulates the cost of one credit per hour. </p>
      </details>
      </br>
      <details>
      <summary> What do I do if I can't rent a scooter? </summary>
        <p> If you cannot rent a scooter even when logged in, please feel free to contact us through email or phone call at +1-800-SCOOT or Info@ValleyScoot.com!  </p>
      </details>
      </br>
      <details>
      <summary> Where can I find the scooters that are available to rent, I don't see them? </summary>
        <p> You can go to our stations page where you can see the scooter availability for each station!  </p>
      </details>
      </br>
      <details>
      <summary> What can I do if I don't like the scooter I rented? </summary>
        <p> You can return the scooter to any station and rent a different one! If none of our scooters are to your statisfaction feel free to contact us! </p>
      </details>
    </br></br></br></br></br>
